{"tid":1924183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"三月十七日起由神根地區抵港需強制檢疫","createTime":"2020-03-13T14:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T14:36:55.000Z","uid":57582,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"63efb8847fa8394213bf267d2c8ed226b41726fe","tid":1924183,"uid":57582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:03:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202003/13/P2020031300782.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202003%2F13%2FP2020031300782.htm&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j8%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=b719b9ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202003/13/P2020031300782.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n  由三月十七日零時零分起，抵港前14日曾到以下國家／地區的人士（不論是否香港居民）需接受家居強制檢疫：<br />\n <br />\n一）韓國（大邱及慶尚北道除外）（亦適用於非香港居民）<br />\n二）歐洲神根地區，即奧地利、比利時、捷克、丹麥、愛沙尼亞、芬蘭、法國、德國、希臘、匈牙利、冰島、意大利（艾米利亞－－羅馬涅、倫巴第及威尼托地區除外）、拉脫維亞、列支敦士登公國、立陶宛、盧森堡、馬耳他、荷蘭、挪威、波蘭、葡萄牙、斯洛伐克共和國、斯洛文尼亞共和國、西班牙、瑞典及瑞士"},{"pid":"0a8e608f3608f49a647db6dabcbf70b20b65fc26","tid":1924183,"uid":133806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:07:38.000Z","msg":"一入就拉，疊起一堆，莫問到hongkong，驗疫執行大行動。唔理肥瘦，請勿進hongkong，遵守入境奉告，強闖者入境隨時係咁歹，帶銀來入境照抨，藏匿者將公刊樣貌，發現會被控，兼大碌竹蹦，傳播者被監禁，之後照踢出hongkong！"},{"pid":"e89209654cb66499029f5544b5b1c54d70c4a634","tid":1924183,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:18:02.000Z","msg":"中國爆左三個禮拜先封<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f1cdecd87dc719378c1e8b6ac25f232f0483ed","tid":1924183,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:27:18.000Z","msg":"反對23條立法聯盟簽署<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeCGhCiDOR4qD8qLEqljYO58qX8Wykq6TxEiyB0fjuZbEigoQ/formResponse\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeCGhCiDOR4qD8qLEqljYO58qX8Wykq6TxEiyB0fjuZbEigoQ%2FformResponse&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j8%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=9c1c25d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeCGhCiDOR4qD8qLEqljYO58qX8Wykq6TxEiyB0fjuZbEigoQ/formResponse</a>"},{"pid":"9f9e5ef1cce2630c6fde64aac8bd4f60373e6d19","tid":1924183,"uid":22554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T14:36:55.000Z","msg":"唔防英國真係痴撚線, 連BORIS JOHNSON 都認國內應該最少有5000人中招, 咁個情況仲緊要過神根地區啦"}]}